<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='11960:11987'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1a0164', 'WYG', '001-22b' );" name="001-22b" class="pb">[001-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='11987:12010'>不勝是年有大水死王三人東北大動晝昏日再中北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='12010:12020'>方有貴人子走於紂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='12020:12039'>既濟九月年大水地臨三年不絶六世多血</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='12039:12066'>未濟有故都破水國來兵四年九月有分國陽殊邑<span class='krp-note'>按/以</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='12066:12113'><span class='krp-note'>上依六十四卦次序各為之辭盖即毖緯之文語多艱/深不可曉而訛脱尤甚據王劭稱貧之二字為真人之</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='12113:12144'><span class='krp-note'>誤則知自隋以前其書已有差錯/今既無别本可證姑仍舊文録之</span></span><br/>
